OL,3,CAnti-terrorism measures considered for
OL,4,Ccity's tourist hotspots
OL,6,FAnti-terrorism measures are being
OL,7,Fconsidered for popular tourist areas
OL,8,Fof Plymouth.
OL,10,FThe Hoe, which overlooks Plymouth
OL,11,FSound and regularly hosts large-scale
OL,12,Fevents, and the Barbican are among the
OL,13,Fareas being considered for an Anti-
OL,14,FTerrorism Traffic Regulation Order
OL,15,F(ATTRO).
