OL,3,CAnti-terrorism measures considered for
OL,4,Ccity's tourist hotspots
OL,6,FThe ATTRO, which was requested by
OL,7,Flocal police, allows emergency
OL,8,Fservices to close off or restrict
OL,9,Faccess to certain areas to improve
OL,10,Fsafety and the response to potential
OL,11,Fthreats.
OL,13,FWhile the ATTRO will only be activated
OL,14,Fwhen needed, it covers a large area -
OL,15,Fincluding Plymouth Hoe, the Barbican
OL,16,Fand nearby locations.
OL,18,F'Having an ATTRO means we're prepared'
OL,19,F- councillor
