OL,3,CAnti-terrorism measures considered for
OL,4,Ccity's tourist hotspots
OL,6,F"Having an ATTRO in place means we're
OL,7,Fprepared to act swiftly to protect
OL,8,Feveryone. It's about being proactive
OL,9,Fand ensuring we have the right tools
OL,10,Fto safeguard our community."
OL,12,FThe council, which wants the public to
OL,13,Fhave their say on the plans, have
OL,14,Fstressed the measures will not impact
OL,15,Fdaily life.
OL,17,FIt will not result in the
OL,18,Fpedestrianisation of any areas, the
OL,19,Finstallation of any permanent barriers
OL,20,For change the current layout of roads
OL,21,Fand public pathways.
