OL,3,CAnti-terrorism measures considered for
OL,4,Ccity's tourist hotspots
OL,6,FCouncillor Mark Coker, who is
OL,7,Fresponsible for strategic planning and
OL,8,Ftransport at the council, added: "The
OL,9,FATTRO will help us manage traffic and
OL,10,Fpedestrian access effectively during
OL,11,Flarge events, ensuring that emergency
OL,12,Fservices can operate without hindrance.
OL,14,F"This is a crucial step in maintaining
OL,15,Fpublic safety and smooth operations in
OL,16,Four city."
OL,18,FAnyone who would like to comment on
OL,19,Fthe proposals should visit Plymouth
OL,20,FCity Council's website.
